-Rice and Pasta
Go on a culinary adventure with one of these Non-traditional Holiday dishes
-Side Dishes
The collection has veganized semi tradional recipes plus adventurous delights
-Main Dishes
Forget the roasted meats or make one for your vegan guests. These mains are creative and delicious.
-Desserts🍰
